          "name": "Research on the Current Website",
          "purpose": "Through a heuristic evaluation with three UX and frontend experts, followed by usability testing with engineers and engineering students using task-based metrics and a System Usability Scale (SUS), several key issues became clear.",

          "findings": [
            {
              "title": "",
              "description": "Important content like software updates, pricing, manuals, and student discounts was difficult to locate."
            },

            {
              "title": "",
              "description": "No search functionality made finding information slow and frustrating."
            },
            {
              "title": "",
              "description": "Users described the site as outdated and unreliable, especially for payments."
            },
            {
              "title": "",
              "description": "Visual design and layout did not meet modern expectations for technical software."
            },
            {
              "title": "",
              "description": "Bundles and discounts were unclear, causing confusion."
            },
            {
              "title": "",
              "description": "Heavy text and weak hierarchy made pages feel overwhelming."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],

